.TH COMMONVOICE-STATUS 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Common Voice Status Manual"
.SH NAME
commonvoice-status - View Mozilla Common Voice statistics per language
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B commonvoice-status
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBcommonvoice-status\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for viewing Mozilla Common Voice recording and validation statistics per language. It displays recorded hours, validated hours, speakers, and sentences. Features include Nordic language comparison, sorting options, gap analysis for reaching milestones, direct contribution links, and local caching with 1-hour TTL.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application
.TP
.B F5
Refresh the current data
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts dialog
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export current view to CSV or JSON format
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/commonvoice-status/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/commonvoice-status/
Cached data.
